snippet.title: GOD VIBRATIONS ~ Trailer !
snippet.description:
https://nodevatall.itch.io/godvibrations

Finally ! GOD VIBRATIONS is a 2D versus platformer for 2-4 players, very much like Smash Bros and Towerfall, where jumpy kawaii gods fights in locations where the ground vibrates to the music. All of that because of a bard who sing stories about deities he doesn't know !
Now the gods are angry, let's get dirty !

Made for the GLOBAL GAME JAM 2017 STRASBOURG ! Thanks for playing and see you next year !

Play it on https://nodevatall.itch.io/godvibrations
